dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Jefferson County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents roads (2021) and Right of Ways (ROW) (2020) for Jefferson County, Wisconsin. While the roads data is current to 2021, the Right of Ways (ROW) data has not been updated since 2020. Both layers were submitted as part of the '2021 WLIP Call for Data' by the Wisconsin Department of Administration and are included here in one geodatabase for the convenience of the user. [Roads: Jefferson County Road Center Lines L = Local Road C = County Road S = State Road P = Private Road I = Interstate F = Federal Road. ROW: The parcel line layer delineates parcel features such as ownership boundaries, roads, water features, easements and others that affect property ownership interests.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
